commit.message:
configure: Regenerate for new libtool.

        * configure: Regenerate for new libtool.
        * Makefile.in: Ditto.
        * include/Makefile.in: Ditto.
        * aclocal.m4: Ditto.

Co-Authored-By: Steve Ellcey <sje@cup.hp.com>

From-SVN: r140706
